text: Laufenthal is a village in the Upper Palatinate (Bavaria, Germany), belonging to Regensburg and the market town of Hemau. Technically a ward of Hemau, Laufenthal is about five kilometers from the town, near the river Laaber. ==Other websites== *Map *Homepage of Schloss Laufenthal *St Ottilia Church Category:Regensburg (district) Category:Villages in Bavaria
